BaggageAllowance.ApplicablePartyText: PTC Type: All except INF (Basically any PTC type that would have their own seat)

WeightAllowance.DescText: No weight limit except the following Origins Singapore, Singapore - Changi International Airport (SIN) carry on should not exceed 15 lbs. (7kgs) Beijing - Beijing Capital International Airport (PEK) Civil Aviation Administration of China (CAAC) requires that domestic hand carry bags should not exceed 10kgs. Individual carrier rules apply for international flights. Shanghai - Pudong International Airport (PVG) carry on should not exceed 22lbs. (10kgs)

DimensionAllowance.DescText: Linear Length: 114 cm or approximately 56 x 35 x 23 cm

PieceAllowance.Desc: 1 carry-on bag and 1 personal item are allowed. Personal Item 1 purse, briefcase, camera bag or diaper bag or 1 laptop computer (computers cannot be checked) or 1 item of a similar or smaller size to those listed above
